      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'M ALRIGHT (1) hit the frame two on end before being rewarded with a deserved win last time, scoring at this track over 272m (15.93). Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. KARLI MULWEE (6) was always well back but did hit the line strongly late to finish 5th and beaten only 5 lengths (16.16) at this track. Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Cannot be underestimated. MY JULIA (3) goes very well at this journey having never missed the frame including two wins and three placings. Hit the frame latest (17.82) when third at Taree Super Track in a Grade 5. Looks one of the chances. IRONIC AUSSIE (4) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
